channel.title: Counter-Strike 2D video game (FREE)
channel.description:
Unreal Software had developed Counter-Strike 2D, a "top down" version of Valve's original game. And it's FREE.
[url]https://www.cs2d.com/index.php[/url]
Top down games don't really interest me, but for the few die-hard CS fans, this may be of some value.
Only 7MB to download. :wink:
